postReview.title: Aston Villa 2-1 Leicester City: Bailey helps hosts return to winning ways
postReview.description: A 76th-minute Leon Bailey goal helped Aston Villa get their first win in three Premier League matches at the expense of Leicester City.

preReview.title: Philogene may leave Aston Villa in January
preReview.description: Jaden Philogene has been in and out at Aston Villa this season, and could be allowed to leave the club in January.
